## ✨ CHANGE 2 — Stories Awareness in Onboarding and Generation

**Goal:** Capture how each user actually posts on each platform (feed vs Stories vs Reels) so VIRL can generate content optimized for their actual workflow.

**Files to modify:** `index.html` (CreatorProfile component + plan generation system prompt)

### 2a. Add per-platform format preferences

When a user selects platforms in their profile, follow up with format preferences for each. After the existing `myPlatforms` chip selector, add:

