  prompt += "\nIMPORTANT: Match the format to the user's actual workflow. If they primarily use Instagram Stories, generate Story-optimized content (short, casual, in-the-moment, with poll/question/tap-through suggestions) — NOT feed posts. If they primarily use carousels, generate carousel-optimized content with slide-by-slide structure. Do not default to video format if the user has not selected video.\n";
}
```

